        {
            "title": "美國貿易代表格裡爾稱 與中國的關係現在以穩定為重",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國貿易代表格裡爾表示，儘管一些盟友敦促對北京採取協調行動，但美國已將穩定與中國的貿易形勢擺在首位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為沒人希望與中國發生全面經濟衝突，而我們也不會，」格裡爾周四在華盛頓舉行的美國成長峰會上表示。「事實上，川普總統有機會利用我們在中國面前的所有籌碼，無論是在軟件、半導體還是其他各種領域，而且我們確實擁有很多籌碼。許多盟友有興趣採取協調行動，但目前的決定是，我們希望保持關係穩定。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-abb1cb7a-6c1b-399c-a78d-bae5af43d012-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">格裡爾聲稱，自川普上任以來，美國對華貿易逆差下降了「約25%」，對於一個致力於平衡商品貿易的團隊來說，這是朝著「正確方向」前進的一步。與此同時，他也承認，中國產品仍在設法流入美國，包括通過其他國家轉運。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「目前，我們希望確保中國購買的是我們就該賣給他們的東西：飛機、化學品、醫療器械和農產品，」他說。「我們可以從他們那裡購買一些非敏感產品。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Greer Says US Prioritizing Stability Over Conflict With China</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E8%A3%A1%E7%88%BE%E7%A8%B1-%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%A5%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E7%82%BA%E9%87%8D-001802794.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 08:55:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華購美大豆步伐緩慢 貝森特疑似放寬期限",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國財長貝森特似乎延長了此前設定的中國採購美國大豆的最後期限，但由於缺乏對中國的新出口銷售，市場仍對北京能否達到目標持懷疑態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特周三表示，中國正向著在2月底前購買1200萬噸美國大豆的方向邁進。這一時間點晚於白宮上個月的聲明，當時稱中國同意在「2025年最後兩個月」採購這一數量的大豆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當被問及大豆採購進度以及距離年底還有多少時間時，貝森特當時澄清說，目標是「季末，所以我認為應該是2月28日」。。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d4ad462f-fc4d-3fef-8682-c8579630f2fc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然延長的幾個月爭取了更多時間，但幾乎沒有跡象表明中國在加快採購。據美國農業部周四的報告，對華大豆出口連續第四日無新增銷售。該機構數據顯示，中國自10月30日以來僅採購了225萬噸大豆。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2UZFEj1PJnsHU2kQitCKvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4853ae8e6a612bdec95372618e2b37cc\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大豆期貨周四在漲跌之間波動。大豆在11月中旬觸及逾一年高位後回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「市場仍然理所當然地持懷疑態度，」StoneX風險管理顧問Matt Campbell在報告中稱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Extends China Soy Deadline But Slow Sales Fuel Doubts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%86%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90%E7%B7%A9%E6%85%A2%E5%BC%95%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90-164109728.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 08:10:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Vanguard稱交易員低估了日本國債殖利率上升的風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/93M6mpip5u6_NYAqrvEzRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/83f2cce8477a5954989806ea1b818751\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> Vanguard Group Inc.表示，交易員押注<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:日本央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/日本央行\">日本央行</a>本月將加息，但他們仍然低估了日本利率可能需要進一步走高以抑制通膨的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於投資者押注日本央行將在12月18日至19日的會議上加息，日本2年期國債殖利率近日突破1%，達到2008年以來最高水平。但經過多年持續寬鬆的貨幣政策，日本利率仍然遠低於G-10其他國家，而且日本通膨期望接近自2004年有記錄以來的最高水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/o1P0Kt5t6CFtllIi8YgkcQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fcebbaafcd333f98ccc6969351642587\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「市場低估了日本要緩解通膨壓力中性利率需要上升的程度，因此減持日本國債是正確的做法，」管理著11萬億美元資產的Vanguard的全球利率主管Roger Hallam周四在接受採訪時表示。「我們仍然認為日本央行將繼續正常化，並將在12月加息。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0d5d8309-b5db-37db-a808-e18fed7784d4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行行長植田和男本周說，中性利率的預估範圍很廣。日本央行此前曾表示，中性利率介於1%至2.5%之間。目前的政策利率為0.50%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Traders Underpricing Risk of Higher Japan Yields, Vanguard Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/vanguard%E7%A8%B1%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E4%BD%8E%E4%BC%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E6%AE%96%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-001748758.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 08:55:54",
